sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant E as Markdown编辑器
    participant W as WebWorker
    participant B as 后端API
    participant T as 火山云TOS

    U->>E: 粘贴图片
    E->>W: 发送图片文件
    W->>W: ImageBitmap加载
    W->>W: OffscreenCanvas绘制
    W->>W: 渐进式压缩(0.8→0.3)
    W-->>E: 返回压缩后的Blob

    E->>B: POST /api/article/upload-presign<br/>fileName, contentType, fileSize
    B->>B: 生成TOS预签名URL
    B-->>E: 返回signedUrl + publicUrl

    E->>T: PUT signedUrl<br/>Content-Type + 文件数据
    T-->>E: 上传成功
    E->>E: 插入Markdown图片语法<br/>![alt](publicUrl)
    E-->>U: 显示图片
